      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title 37, United States Code, to require the Secretary concerned to pay a member in the reserve component of an Armed Force a special bonus or incentive pay in the same amount as a member in the regular component of that Armed Force.</title>
